annotation.table_summary: This table presents the Consolidated Statements of Operations for Apple Inc. for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2025, September 28, 2024, and September 30, 2023, showing the breakdown of net sales, costs, expenses, and resulting profitability metrics.

row_summaries.description: This row shows the net sales from Products for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the net sales from Services for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the total net sales, which is the sum of Products and Services sales, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the cost of sales for Products for each of the three fiscal years.

This row shows the total cost of sales, which is the sum of the cost of sales for Products and Services, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the gross margin, calculated as total net sales minus total cost of sales, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the research and development operating expense for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the selling, general and administrative operating expense for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the total operating expenses, which is the sum of research and development and selling, general and administrative expenses, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the operating income, calculated as gross margin minus total operating expenses, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the net amount of other income and expense for each of the three fiscal years.

row_summaries.row_label: Income before provision for income taxes
row_summaries.description: This row shows the income before provision for income taxes, calculated as operating income plus other income/(expense), net, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the provision for income taxes for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the net income, calculated as income before provision for income taxes minus the provision for income taxes, for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the basic earnings per share for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the diluted earnings per share for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the number of basic shares used in computing earnings per share for each of the three fiscal years.
This row shows the number of diluted shares used in computing earnings per share for each of the three fiscal years.
